85 Alabama 1975, are not satisfied.
86 Section 3. It is the intent of the Legislature that,
87 pursuant to Section 150 of the Constitution of Alabama of
88 2022, the Supreme Court of Alabama shall amend its rules to
89 conform with this act.
90 Section 4. This act shall become effective on October
91 1, 2026.
